8. Webinar Strategy

The Dual CTA Structure
Every Blueprint webinar presents two offers simultaneously — not either/or but a natural ascension:

	•	CTA 1 — AI Launch Blueprint (~$997): Start implementing AI in your business right now
	•	CTA 2 — Live Event Upgrade: Come do this with me in person for one full day — seats limited to 40

The live event creates urgency that helps sell the Blueprint. People who aren't ready to travel buy the digital version instead of leaving empty-handed.

Webinar Pitch Script — Presenting Both Offers
"There are two ways to be in the room.
The first is the full Saturday experience — 40 seats, one day, you leave with everything running.
The second is the full weekend VIP experience — you get Saturday plus a private strategy day Sunday with me and a small group of serious operators. Only 12 of those exist.
If you know you want VIP, grab it first because those will go before the general seats do."

The Marblism Webinar vs. Blueprint Webinar
	•	Marblism webinar: Good for list building, positioning, and Marblism affiliate commissions. NOT the primary vehicle to $2.5M.
	•	Blueprint webinar: The primary revenue driver. Sells Blueprint program AND live event seats. Must run on rotation separate from Marblism.



